/>\n祈求達哥萬歲 達朝萬歲  未忘掉派對<br />\n明天  再度伴隨  一秒破命時  再沒有憂慮 <br />\n閒時  直來直去   達哥絕句  突然又對對<br />\n暴君    卻又為誰   深宵獨自亂吹<br />\n期求有天  再跟隊<br />\n<br />\n分分秒秒都散播   未怕險阻<br />\n瘋瘋顛顛不說破   但很清楚<br />\n皇恩  感激打機   得到你附和<br />\n夜深還有你  去陪我直播<br />\n<br />\n那日全滅有點早<br />\n波叔也尚算安好<br />\n最終喝著汽水 極其自然般 拉了布 <br />\n<br />\n祈求達哥萬歲 達朝萬歲  未忘掉派對<br />\n留低一個敵人   等你隊冧時   你卻已很累<br />\n原來   路途樂趣   並無絕對    共遺下興趣<br />\n而今  壯志未酬  竟敢獨自離隊<br />\n遺下弟兄去媾女<br />\n<br />\n仍然未能共進未能共退 突然便撤退<br />\n曾經一再諾言今生有達朝再沒有憂慮<br />\n為何淚流下去未留下去 未重拾過去<br />\n暴君這個壞人偏卻冷酷如許<br />\n原來昨天  已收隊"},{"pid":"715c72bca3e881667ec62ccf534a4d9f21326515","tid":729402,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67db222c31559175c2cbbb3c83aa4b9d11e7a3ca","tid":729402,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc39000dae0a6fd0e7d9bbafbcd737f49a664976","tid":729402,"uid":72533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:13:06.000Z","msg":"推到達哥自己唱"},{"pid":"a0ac51ad2d5612d23179fb7ba3ed23b56e06bc99","tid":729402,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535332bf8def06f3315aca0bfb623fbac62ee049","tid":729402,"uid":43222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a9ea95b561d910efcb61812032f1485f77009c","tid":729402,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fafab478c1be479a49fb70d1c68c47594f1c3f4","tid":729402,"uid":171602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply